{"tid":687094,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有多少「奇女子」？","createTime":"2018-06-02T02:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T13:25:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3af459b4707b44bf3523112d115a967a514a859e","tid":687094,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180602/20408411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408411&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=202aadc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408411&h=6da3990e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180602/20408411</a><br />\n<br />\n香港有多少「奇女子」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180602/large/e8909a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180602%2Flarge%2Fe8909a.jpg&h=d8652936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本港一個公屋富婆，網戀「馬來西亞金融分析師」，成為對方提款機，一年半時間，匯款三百多次，被騙2,640萬港幣。也就是說，她差不多每天都在匯錢，每次平均約7萬。真奇怪，世上竟有這麼癡心的人。既然不介意用金錢去換取「愛意」，每次7萬，還怕買不到韓星面孔的小鮮肉？或者出錢把男人帶去韓國，整一個山寨版金城武，重賞之下必有勇夫，左擁金城武，右抱木村拓哉應該都不是夢想。何必跟空氣拍拖？<br />\n<br />\n不過這單新聞最奇情的不是公屋富婆的愛情觀，而是她的身家。2,640萬中，據說只有100多萬是富婆本人的積蓄，其他的錢，都是借的，不是問朋友借，就是從銀行借。也就是說，這個奇女子總共借了約2,540萬元。<br />\n正在閱讀這篇文章的人，你們之中，有多少人能夠借到這樣一筆錢呢？<br />\n<br />\n我不知道公屋富婆的朋友是甚麼人，有錢人的錢，不會以現金形式放在牀底，對有錢人來說，錢是用來生錢的工具。把可以用來投資的錢借給別人，最大的可能性便是相信後者的還錢能力，並且，後者有能力支付可觀回報。<br />\n<br />\n至於銀行，沒有抵押品，銀行不會借錢給人。假如你有一層樓，銀行可以借出的錢是樓價七成，但上限500萬，若你仍有按揭未還，需扣除按揭。能夠借到手的現金有限。<br />\n一個公屋女子，借得到2,540萬，比被騙2,640萬更離奇。而香港有多多少少這樣的奇女子呢？  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2e3abf4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n獨家料逐日爆 (陳惜姿)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n夢與現實 (邁克)"},{"pid":"6b9fd9762d50c6d317910d36250ec24734205e47","tid":687094,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"奇廢老仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30387265296b6aeb7ac0910b16681d7c2c5db13","tid":687094,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ed2e57c416a5896e88358bc19b0240eef748df","tid":687094,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"單野有鬼"},{"pid":"1f03370d4b12366366b94597c5cdd9f90cb0e2e3","tid":687094,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b24a047f78a802f121d7bb031901a782c36abc3","tid":687094,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"根本呃公屋住 、除非買左 、唔係肯定一身蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5927d2201f12807c62715eac8a7ae502efaf5ab2","tid":687094,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"最簡單 借完錢老破收埋D錢 再話比人呃左<br />\n潛水幾年之後 fat fat"},{"pid":"fbb2f13fb9c0ad0a750876afb72b8a04dfcd1cb5","tid":687094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"狄娜"},{"p